data.title: We're over a year away from our movie's release with still 4 weeks left of shooting, but the Paramount Studios global marketing strategy...
data.meta_description:
218K likes, 600 comments - therock on April 20, 2016: "We're over a year away from our movie's release with still 4 weeks left of shooting, but the Paramount Studios global marketing strategy has already begun. 
Just went thru this coffee table book sized concept art for billboards, posters, digital etc. 
I like the overall concepts and think you guys will too. Some cool, bad ass and funny stuff!

We're the #Avengers of the beach (minus all the cool super powers and flying around sh*t) mixed with enough rated R raunch comedy that'll make one of my boyhood heroes, Richard Pryor very proud.

#BAYWATCH MAY 19, 2017.

I put the laptop in the shot to make it look intellectual.".
